<bold>Y</bold>(<italic>t</italic>)+<bold>ε</bold>; <italic>s.d.</italic> is a standard deviation), <italic>I</italic>(<italic>k</italic>) is an identity <italic>k</italic>×<italic>k</italic> matrix.</p>
