</p>
      </sec>
      <sec id="Sec10">
        <title>Data preparation</title>
        <p>At the data preparation stage, the longitudinal dataset is preprocessed with the following command:</p>
        <p>
          <graphic xlink:href="12859_2017_1538_Figa_HTML.gif" id="MO1"/>
        </p>
        <p>Here longdat.csv is a path to the longitudinal dataset (i.e., can be csv or SAS data file). Names of specific covariates can be explicitly mentioned:</p>
